description:
Chic hotel with classic British hospitality near stations

Near New Street Station

On the east side of Birmingham, Hotel La Tour is a 10-minute walk from New Street Train Station, with airport-bound trains running every 15 minutes. Bullring Shopping Centre is only a 3-minute walk south, or you can hop on one of the many buses running down Moor or Park streets.

Innovative Science Museum

Millennium Park's Thinktank Science Museum and Giant Screen provide a stimulating break from shopping at Bullring's 160 stores. For entertainment, you can walk 10 minutes to Chinatown and the Theatre District, where the Arcadian complex offers comedy and a nightclub.

Best of British cuisine

After an invigorating gym workout you might indulge in afternoon tea with homemade scones and clotted cream, finger sandwiches, and maybe a treacle tart. Mr White's Chophouse and Alvar Bar specialize in British and French fusion cuisine with options to dine alfresco or inside.

Room service and WiFi

You can sink into an armchair or premium bedding and order a bottle of wine from room service while watching some TV on the 32-inch flat-screen. In all 174 guestrooms, you have free WiFi, rainfall showerheads, and a digital control panel to dim the lights from bed.

HOTEL_AMENITY.value:
The hotel offers a restaurant. A bar/lounge is on site where guests can unwind with a drink. High-speed wireless Internet access is complimentary. This business-friendly hotel also offers a fitness center, a terrace, and tour/ticket assistance. Onsite parking is available (surcharge).

Hotel La Tour is a smoke-free property.

DINING.value:
Buffet breakfasts are available for a surcharge and are served each morning between 6:30 AM and 11 AM.
Mr White's Chophouse - This brasserie specializes in British cuisine and serves lunch and dinner. Guests can enjoy drinks at the bar. A children's menu is available. Open daily.
Alvar Bar - This bar specializes in British cuisine and serves lunch and light fare. Open daily.
24-hour room service is available.

CHECK_IN_POLICY.value:
Extra-person charges may apply and vary depending on hotel policy.
Government-issued photo identification and a credit card or cash deposit are required at check-in for incidental charges.
Special requests are subject to availability upon check-in and may incur additional charges. Special requests cannot be guaranteed.
